      "raw_text": "The matter of affiliating the\nteamsters' union with the Spokane\nbuilding trades department of the\nAmerican Federation of Labor will\nlikely be taken up again at the\nnext meeting of the Spokane Sec\ntional Central Labor council Mon\nday night. Cold weather Of the\nlast two days has greatly impeded\nthe work of the teamsters and many\nof them are again out of work and\nwaiting for better weather"
